snippet.title: RC Rush Game Trailer
snippet.description: RC Rush is an exciting arcade racing game featuring radio controlled trucks. Win races to unlock career events, compete in head to head battles to unlock new vehicles, and level up your way to becoming the ultimate RC champion!
